-- Bombardier Mulls Part-Sale of Aerospace Unit, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-02-07T07:17:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-07/bombardier-mulls-part-sale-of-aerospace-unit-handelsblatt-says.html
Bombardier Inc. (BBD/B)  is looking at a part-
sale of its aerospace unit to Commercial Aircraft Corp. of
 China ,  Handelsblatt  reported, without saying where it got the
information.  The Canadian company is “developing new relationships with
the Chinese aviation industry” and “considering many different
types of agreements,” an unidentified Bombardier spokeswoman
told the German newspaper. An agreement can be expected in the
near future, Handelsblatt cited her as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
